latestIgtvVideos.title: Hair Transformation ✂️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
.
Yes, you guys read it right. I let my sister cut my hair 🙄 

I wanted to do this for so long 🤩 as far as I remember I always had long hair and I personally adore long hairs but it was about time to have some change💁🏻‍♀️ so I decided to cut them short💇🏻‍♀️ and I didn't have any guts to do it on my own so I insisted my sister to do it for me. At first I was so scared but she cut them so beautifully that I am in love with my new hair now🧡 

🎶Song : tay money- bussin
